    </div>
    <div class="product_faq-items block-flex-wrap">
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Does LegitGrails Authentication Work?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            LegitGrails follows a meticulous authentication process to verify the legitimacy of your Hugo Boss items. Select the product category and your preferred response time on our platform. Next, upload clear, high-quality photos focusing on details like labels, stitching, logos, and unique design elements. 
            <br><br>
            Our advanced AI technology conducts an initial scan, followed by a thorough review from our team of experienced experts. This dual-layer verification process ensures a high degree of accuracy. Once completed, you’ll receive a detailed verdict and a personalized certificate of authenticity, giving you confidence in your Hugo Boss purchase.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Long Does LegitGrails Authentication Take?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            We understand the need for swift authentication. LegitGrails offers flexible response times to fit your schedule, including 24-hour, 12-hour, 2-hour, and even 30-minute options. Simply choose the timeframe that best suits your needs, and our team will ensure your Hugo Boss item is verified within your selected period, delivering fast and reliable results.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Who Owns Hugo Boss Today?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15">
          <p class="small-text">
            Hugo Boss AG is a publicly traded company listed on the Frankfurt Stock Exchange. As of 2023, its ownership is structured as follows:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Free Float (Public Investors): Around 83% of the shares are held by institutional and individual investors.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Marzotto Family Holdings: Through entities like PFC S.r.l. and Zignago Holding S.p.A., the Marzotto family owns approximately 15% of the company.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Treasury Shares: Hugo Boss retains around 2% of its own shares.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="small-text">This diversified ownership ensures broad investor participation and financial stability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">What’s the Difference Between Hugo and Boss?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15">
          <p class="small-text">
            Hugo Boss has strategically divided its brand into two distinct labels to cater to different demographics:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">BOSS: Designed for millennials aged 25-40, BOSS focuses on refined, smart, and tailored clothing for business and formal occasions. It emphasizes classic wardrobe essentials with a modern edge.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">HUGO: Targeted at Gen Z consumers under 25, HUGO embraces trend-driven, fashion-forward styles. This line features bold, youthful designs and casual wear, appealing to a more contemporary, street-style aesthetic.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="small-text">Both brands uphold Hugo Boss’s high standards of quality, differing primarily in style and target audience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Are Hugo Boss Suits High-Quality?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Yes, Hugo Boss suits are known for their exceptional quality. The brand prioritizes expert craftsmanship, premium fabrics, and meticulous tailoring techniques. This dedication ensures that their suits offer a refined aesthetic, superior durability, and an impeccable fit, making them a top choice for those seeking sophistication and elegance in formalwear.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">What Is Hugo Boss Famous For?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Hugo Boss is internationally recognized for its premium fashion, particularly in men’s and women’s apparel, accessories, and fragrances. The brand is synonymous with sharp tailoring, especially in its suit collections, and has a strong presence in the luxury fashion industry. Over time, Hugo Boss has expanded its offerings to include casual wear, sportswear, and lifestyle products, maintaining its reputation for quality craftsmanship and contemporary design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Who Founded Hugo Boss and What Is Its History?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
           Hugo Boss was founded in 1924 by Hugo Ferdinand Boss in Metzingen, Germany. Initially, the company produced general-purpose clothing. In the 1930s, it supplied uniforms for the Nazi regime, a chapter that has been critically examined in historical discussions. Following World War II and the founder’s passing in 1948, the company shifted its focus to producing high-end men’s suits. Over the decades, Hugo Boss evolved into a global fashion powerhouse, now offering a wide range of apparel, accessories, and fragrances across more than 1,400 retail locations worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">What Makes Hugo Boss Expensive?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15">
          <p class="small-text">
            Several factors contribute to the premium pricing of Hugo Boss products:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">High-Quality Materials: The brand selects premium fabrics to ensure comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Superior Craftsmanship: Expert tailoring and meticulous attention to detail enhance the fit and finish of each piece.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Prestigious Brand Image: As a luxury fashion house, Hugo Boss carries a reputation that adds to its perceived value.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="small-text">Innovative Design: Continuous investment in contemporary and timeless designs appeals to a broad and discerning customer base.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="small-text">These elements collectively justify the higher price point associated with Hugo Boss products, making them a worthwhile investment for those who appreciate premium fashion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class="product_faq-btns block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden">
        <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="rebranding_btn">
